Flexy - A tool to inflect and in other ways "flex" words

and

greek.py - Rules for inflection of greek words based on http://www.komvos.edu.gr/dictionaries/triantafyllidis/TriLegent.htm (same as http://www.greek-language.gr/greekLang/modern_greek/tools/lexica/triantafyllides/index.html )
Adjectives: http://www.greek-language.gr/greekLang/modern_greek/tools/lexica/onomatiko/adjectives.html
Nouns: http://www.greek-language.gr/greekLang/modern_greek/tools/lexica/onomatiko/nouns.html
Verbs: http://www.greek-language.gr/greekLang/modern_greek/tools/lexica/rimatiko/general.html

USAGE

./flexy.py <word> <rule id> [<rules filename>]

